==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Diddle
<hw>Did"dle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Daddle</er>.]</ety> <def>To totter, as a child in walking.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Quarles.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Diddle</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Diddle
<hw>Did"dle</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Perh. from AS.
<ets>dyderian</ets> to deceive, the letter <it>r</it> being changed to
<it>l</it>.]</ety> <def>To cheat or overreach.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark> <rj><au>Beaconsfield.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Diddler</ent>⟦br⟧
